  "informal_statement": "Twice the dot product of two plane vectors is at most the sum of their squared norms (2 u·v ≤ |u|² + |v|²).",
  "informal_proof_idea": "|u|² + |v|² - 2u·v = |u - v|² = (x1-x2)² + (y1-y2)² ≥ 0. nlinarith with the two square hints.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem two_dot_le (x1 y1 x2 y2 : ℝ) : 2 * (x1 * x2 + y1 * y2) ≤ (x1 ^ 2 + y1 ^ 2) + (x2 ^ 2 + y2 ^ 2)",
